ygData.messageBody:
Lake of Ill Omen.

I went to Kunark at level 19 and have worked my way up to Level 26, mostly
in the Lake, but also in Warsliks Wood, fighting Forest Giants.
I am ready now to go to Frontier Mountains.

The hardest part of Kunark is getting through Firiona Vie without
being slaughtered by the spiders.

If you can, get someone to invis you. SOme see thorugh invisibile,
but most don't.
